title: Favorite Finals Moments and More with Carl Tart

description:
Miles and Jack were joined by writer/actor Carl Tart on the latest episode of Mad Boosties. The trio broke down predictions for Warriors vs Celtics, before discussing some of Carl’s favorite Finals moments and matchups.
